### Create a new Product
POST http://localhost:3055/v1/ecommerce/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": {
    "productId": 101,
    "code": "APPLE_IPHONE_15_PRO_256",
    "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
    "brand": "Apple",
    "description": "The latest iPhone with a powerful A17 Bionic chip and a new titanium design.",
    "release_date": "2023-09-22T00:00:00.000Z",
    "spec": [
      { "k": "Storage", "v": "256GB" },
      { "k": "Color", "v": "Natural Titanium" },
      { "k": "Display", "v": "6.1-inch Super Retina XDR display" }
    ]
  }
}

### Create a new Inventory entry
POST http://localhost:3055/v1/ecommerce/inventories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inventory": {
    "productId": 101,
    "quantity": 50,
    "reservations": []
  }
}

### Add a product to the cart
POST http://localhost:3055/v1/ecommerce/carts/add-product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 123,
  "productId": 101,
  "quantity": 1
}


